Demo Script:

1. Before starting the processes:
You need to reset the state of the "ListS3" process.
- Right Click on "ListS3"
- Click "View State"
- Click on "Clear State"

2. Start "Queues Clean Up" then stop it.

3. Change Rate from the "ControlRate" process
 - Simulate ingest rate of 100 KB or  1 MB

4. Enable Controller Services

5. Select All (except Queues Cleanup )processes 
and "Start"
